lead_paragraph: FIFA presidential candidate Jerome Champagne has protested to soccer's world governing body about the number of observers allowed into the hall for Friday's election, saying he believed they were working for his rivals.

headline.print_headline: FIFA Candidate Champagne Protests Over Election Observers
